https://www.buildthatwebsite.com/elementor-media-query


Prepend your code with 

body[data-elementor-device-mode="desktop"], 

body[data-elementor-device-mode="tablet"], or 

ody[data-elementor-device-mode="mobile"]. So you put a space after and then your code. Something like:

body[data-elementor-device-mode="tablet"] .my-class {
color: red;
}
